BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:Iqg2dNuyeXj5jvhY5RrHI
SUMMARY:Business Over Lunch
DTSTAMP:20260318T064958Z
DTSTART:20260318T113000Z
DESCRIPTION:Know Your Customer\\\, Grow Your Community: How to Attract\\\, 
	Serve\\\, and Keep the Right Audience \\nOrder your tickets HERE! \\nTopic
	 Description:\\nUnderstanding your audience is the foundation of effective
	 marketing\\\, sales\\\, and customer experience—but many small business o
	wners are still trying to speak to “everyone.” This session helps entrepre
	neurs clearly identify who their ideal customer is\\\, what they truly nee
	d\\\, and how to connect with them in an authentic way. Attendees will lea
	ve with clarity and confidence to align their messaging\\\, offers\\\, and
	 outreach with the people they’re best equipped to serve. \\nWhy Attend (V
	alue Points): \\n\\nClarify who your ideal customer actually is—and who th
	ey are not\\nIdentify customer pain points that drive buying decisions\\nS
	trengthen your messaging so it resonates instead of getting ignored\\nBuil
	d deeper trust and loyalty with the right audience\\nImprove marketing res
	ults without increasing your budget\\nReduce overwhelm by focusing your ef
	forts more strategically\\nAlign your products or services with real custo
	mer needs\\nIncrease referrals by serving a clearly defined community\\n\\
	nGain confidence in how you show up and communicate your value\n\nhttps://
	discovermagnolia.org/event/business-over-lunch/\n\nFrom Discover Magnolia
URL:https://discovermagnolia.org/event/business-over-lunch/
LOCATION:Aegis Living at Rodgers Park\\\, 2900 3rd Ave W\\\, Seattle\\\, WA
	\\\, 98119\\\, United States
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:discover-magnolia
CATEGORIES:Discover Magnolia
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT2H
END:VEVENT
